# Place your image assets here.
#
# The spec example references:
#   /memes/pepe.webp
#   /memes/cat.png
#
# The astro-demo overrides these with inline SVG data URIs via the `assets`
# prop on <Markdy />, so this directory is not strictly required to run the
# demo.  Replace the data URIs with real image files here when you have them.
